This directory contains tests for cartoweb using HttpUnit

To learn more about HttpUnit, you can go there:

http://httpunit.sourceforge.net/

If you want to run the HttpUnit test from java, 
 you can type (in this directory):

java -classpath httpunit_all.jar:bin CartowebTest CARTOCLIENT_URL

where CARTOCLIENT_URL is the url of your cartoclient, like for instance:

http://www.example.com/path/to/client.php

If you want to develop these tests, you can edit the .java files in this
directory, and type "make" to recompile.

Alternaly, if you are using Eclipse, you can import this directory as an 
eclipse project.

